ent-RMCGunRackL90A1Empty-name = L90A1 gun rack
ent-RMCGunRackL90A1Empty-desc = A large, heavy-duty rack designed to store L90A1 rifles - locked, loaded, waiting to be fired at a moment's notice. Officially, RCM legislations advise against this practice, but it doesn't stop many armories from keeping their rifles stowed in such a condition.

